Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiting gets us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a step forward into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a deduction and love countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The words "red, white and yellow" written in a diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are an important hint to solving the riddle of a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? There's nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there are zero requests today as well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it's good that things are peaceful, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would be calling me at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi, Cool Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your classes just got finished, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called your cellphone several times but it wouldn't connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that "Shiranpuri" case, my cellphone broke\Ndown for good and I had to buy a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With all that's happened, I decided to\Nstart anew and got a new number also.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:03:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, as appropriate, I informed that girl who's\Ninfiltrating the Organization about the new number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I got a call from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they were off guard for a bit, so it was a fairly short call, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was able to tell me this quite clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Organization has activated a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An agent who is frighteningly skilled at intelligence\Ngathering as well as observation and discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Codename:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all she could tell me in our short conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from her harsh tone, that agent is pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And most likely their target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl with the brown-dyed hair,\Nknown to the Organization as Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expect so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as the FBI is concerned, we'd like to assign a bodyguard to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if we do that now, we would be in danger of\Nletting them know her whereabouts instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the short term, it seems it'd be better to\Navoid that risk and put our trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, be vigilant and protect her closely for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if anything happens, be sure and contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Codename...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with this rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about a game at the Professor's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you're going to discuss\Nwith the Professor when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That phone call just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was from Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and the FBI, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was nothing for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"For me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're hiding something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I mean it's not like another case occurred or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case between Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, behind them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, to summarize your story, first year\Nstudent from class A, Sugiura Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father is the landlord of a small apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That apartment building has three residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one of those three has been behaving suspiciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you want us Detective Boys\Nto find out what he's been doing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's stay over at this guy's place\Ntonight and we can all keep watch on that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds good. Tomorrow is Saturday, so there's no school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, today is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because tonight's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night I play Othello with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:06:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why earlier you put your request in the shoe\Nbox after we had all left for home, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you wouldn't miss your chance to play with your father today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in that case, we wouldn't have gotten\Nyour letter until next week Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so? What kind of suspicious things is that person doing at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, come over and stay at my house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be better if you could see for yourself, Kuroshi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! If it's all right, why don't you come during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to show you my room and the inside of the apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we all go at noon tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My house is in the apartment building called\N"Mokubasou" at Beika City, 2nd district, number 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow, Kuroshi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come it's just Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's that "Kuroshi" thing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was just trying to say "yoroshiku" (thanks).
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Mokubasou" at Beika City, 2nd district, number 23...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Do you recognize it? That apartment building?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's somewhere near the Professor's house though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pass in front of that apartment building a lot on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's old and small, but it's a nice agreeable building.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika City...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2nd district...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Number 23...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Mokubasou."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been completely burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I did hear the sounds of sirens during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what about that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was caught in the fire and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that boy Kaito is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got a few burns, but he was rescued by one of the firemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:25.01,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga\N{\fs11}Police HQ Division One Investigations\NChief Arson Investigator
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's asleep at the hospital now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're the boy from Mouri's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you since that "Red Horse" case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That happened a while ago when Hattori Heiji had come to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person in charge of that murder/arson\Ncase was this guy, Inspector Yuminaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, did anyone die in this fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happily, there were no fatalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s father was badly burned and is in the ICU now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the rest of that boy's family and the other residents of this\Napartment building were all able to get away during the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy's mother happened to be away on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I called her at her hotel earlier, she was\Nastonished and said she was coming back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the three other residents, all three of them\Nhappened to be out at around the time of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they didn't come back until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't the fire happen in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 2:30 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the three of them aren't kids, so there's nothing suspicious\Nabout them going out in the evening and staying out all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's got to be one of those three who set the fire, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told us that one of those three\Npeople was doing suspicious things at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we came here to investigate,\Nwe found that this had happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this in the remains of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. The last page says July 4th. That's yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The weather has been bad since this morning. I have to get up\Nearly or I'll miss school, but I bet the red guy can sleep in late."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does this "red guy" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When I got back from school, I fell down in the entryway."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm glad the white guy was just coming out."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tonight the red guy and the white guy\Nand the yellow guy are all going out."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My dad and I are alone together. I want to play some more but the\Ndetective club is coming tomorrow, so I should go to bed early."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Who is it? Someone came home in the middle of the night."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He's arguing with my father."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's the yellow guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I wonder if my dad found out about the suspicious things he's doing."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's scary, so I'll cover my ears and go to bed. When\NI wake up I'll have to tell Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} about this."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's obvious that the yellow guy set the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of people are those three residents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, sorry about this, but could you\Nbring those three over here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A glare that impales its prey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pressure that's eating into my guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A member of the Organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A member of the Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could they be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to get away from here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else everyone will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, would you mind answering a\Nfew more questions from my officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one of those three was the suspicious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to see Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to ask him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Couldn't you have mentioned that earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do those three people do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the right:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:12.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Hosoi Ryuuhei (25)\NCarpenter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:12.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The one with the band-aid is a carpenter, Hosoi Ryuuhei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:17.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The one with the glasses is a graduate student, Okiya Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:17.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)} Okiya Subaru (27)\NGraduate Student
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:22.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And the heavy one is a part-time worker, Makabe Ginya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:22.48,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Makabe Ginya (29)\NPart-Timer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose one of those three is the yellow guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, what's that? The "yellow guy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Read this for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a diary that the landlord's son wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to that, for some reason, on the\Nday before the fire it seems Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asked these kids to investigate one of the\Nresidents who was behaving questionably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not just kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the highly-respected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he referred to them that way in his diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm inclined to think he's using colors to stand\Nfor the residents of this apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to what's written here, it seems certain that whichever\Nresident is the "yellow guy" is the culprit, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, however, we don't know which of them is the "yellow guy".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of the three have a color in their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody is wearing yellow clothing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their jobs are carpenter, student, and temp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing there that's associated with a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red, white, and yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's like the colors of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a black guy though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A black person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, that dark-skinned man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, if it's the color of their skin, then that\Nguy with the glasses is white, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's ask them a bit more detailed\Nquestions and see what we find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such as who is the certain "yellow" person in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to say the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the night of the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was out drinking with my boss and my\Nsuperiors from the carpentry trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But earlier when we were confirming that, it seems\Nyou left sometime after 1 o'clock in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't been drinking in a long time, so I got really drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To try to sober up, I went off by myself and\Nlaid down on a bench and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, when I came to, it was already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then at the time of the fire, around 2:30 in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means there was nobody with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That band-aid on your face. Did you get in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's OK, just answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got hit by a board while I was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still a beginner, so I keep getting injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are all from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Color?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blue of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cause I like to go surfing occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was driving by myself that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do that frequently whenever I start going crazy\Ntrying to prepare my thesis for my professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whereabouts did you go driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I drove down that tree-lined street by the Teimuzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I'm looking at the greenery, my heart\Nfeels at ease, so I end up along there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I water the plants in the garden at\Nthis apartment building every day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because the landlord doesn't seem\Nvery interested in maintaining the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, then your favorite color is green or something then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you force me to pick one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It covers up the things inside of me\Nthat I don't want to be know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for the same reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Black is the color I hate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night I went to see a movie in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an all-night showing from\N10PM at night until 5AM in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a triple feature from the "Monster Gomera" series.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:16:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My net friend was supposed to go with\Nme, but he suddenly couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's a "net friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, as a side-line, I work as a day trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some friends who exchange information\Nwith me about that on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A day trader? So you deal with stocks and such?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just sort of a hobby, so I only make\Na ridiculously small amount of profit from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your only a part-time worker, but you earn enough\Nto cover your living expenses from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'm registered with a temp agency for daily work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you do public construction work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, there's a lot of mud under your finger nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's mud from the time I played a survival game a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I was running around in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since they got covered in that bright color\Nfrom paint gun shells, I ruined my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then your favorite color is the color that camouflage\Nclothing is usually made from, navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's navy green.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do our favorite colors have something to do with the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsuburaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you help me with a little something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay like that and walk backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walk backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to keep looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one I sensed that pressure from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A member of the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to figure out who it is right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else these kids will get mixed up in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only scraped a little skin off my elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This band-aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My boss told me that since I keep getting\Ninjured I should always carry some.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume it doesn't mean their favorite color,\Nwhat does it mean? This "yellow guy".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it dangerous to keep on concentrating on a kid's diary like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might possibly just be an imaginary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a guy who was doing suspicious things at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't think it sounded like he made it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, whenever you police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a child who's done something bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you start by asking the adults around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they know what kind of child he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:19:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the converse true also?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he's a child, Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has observed the residents\Nclosely, even going so far as to give them nicknames.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Adventure of the Copper Beeches, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the case of the Adventure of the Copper Beeches...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was one of the lines that Holmes said to Dr. Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My dear Watson, you as a medical man are continually gaining\Nlight as to the tendencies of a child by the study of the parents."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Don't you see that the converse is equally valid."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You like Holmes too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to have all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they've all burned up now, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, speaking of Holmes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have ignored this diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I look at that diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you found something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:20:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were in the area near Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pile of mini-cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mini-cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not strange for there to be some miniature cars in a child's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there were quite a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Easily more than 100 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The characters for "Edogawa" have been erased and\Nrewritten several times. The paper's even gotten a bit dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have been trying to write it in kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you can faintly see what looks like katakana underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be "Kuroshi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier when I called the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s mother said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The really smart boy who solved a case that happened at\Nschool instantly is coming over to our house tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seemed really happy when he told her that over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he was called Kuroshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said "Kuroshi" yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was talking about Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would he call him "Kuroshiro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to wait until Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} gets better...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And ask him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall I be Kuroshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And make plain what's black and white right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you which one among them is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The yellow arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd gone out the night of the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And returned home in the morning, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, then somebody must be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which of these three people is the yellow arsonist?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! Over there now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.30,0:24:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi came home?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.08,0:24:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.46,0:24:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mini-car
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.85,0:24:54.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.93,0:24:51.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A dish made from the skin of pigs' ears?\N[mimi no kawa (ear skin) is a pun on mini-car]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:52.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's mimigaa.\N[Okinawa cuisine]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.92,0:24:54.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is that for your father?
